reviewText: A group of beautiful women fight for money for the entertainment of rich folks aboard a luxury ship and the loser is raped viciously infront of everyone. The fight scenes could have been much better and quite frankly it's the gang rape of the woman that made me disgusted. Overexaggerated sex scenes left me digusted as well. If these acts were willing I'd give it a better rating, but it's just vile the way it plays out.
